title: Ranked Sound issue
body: I recently jumped into a game of ranked and during the champion selection i noticed that you could hear when the music would loop back around and sounded similar to a futuristic ship engine.  It was very odd to say the least.

replies.body: We are getting several report about this and we'll fix it ASAP. Thanks!
Hahaha yeah! I was bout to post about this. I frequently get the loop of drumming music lol. Sounds like Rengar's login music.
